org.postgresql.jdbc2

接口 ArrayAssistant

  • 所有已知实现类:
    UUIDArrayAssistant

    public interface ArrayAssistant
    Implement this interface and register the its instance to ArrayAssistantRegistry, to let Postgres driver to support more array type
